name: Dr Marine
discription: Dr Marine is a board-certified obstetrician-gynecologist with Advanced Obstetrics and Gynecology, LLC in Flemington, NJ and is affiliated with Hunterdon Medical Center. She earned a Bachelor of Science in Chemistry and a Bachelor of Arts in French, graduating summa cum laude, from Ohio University in Athen, Ohio.
